title: Ep. 566 - Sundarlal In A Fraud Case - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundarlal meets Daya on the way to the airport. Daya tries to hide Sundar in her house. Jethalal informs about the fraud case Sudar is in.

title: Ep. 567 - Daya In A Dilemma - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal puts Daya in a dilemma where she has to choose between him and Sundar. Daya and Tapu help Sundar sneak into Tapu's room. Jethalal warns them not to let him in, in his house.

title: Ep. 568 - Tapu And Daya Help Sundar - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu helps Sundar hide in his room. Jethalal consistently warns Daya about not letting Sundar in his house. Gokuldham expresses its view on Holi and colors.

title: Ep. 569 - The Peek - A - Boo Game - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundar tries to hide from Jethalal. Jethalal, however, saw him in the kitchen and thinks of him as a thief and informs the whole Gokuldham. People start looking for the thief but to their dismay, they found no one.

title: Ep. 570 - Popatlal To The Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jorawar comes to Gokuldham looking for Sundar and searches for him in Jethalal's house. He keeps an eye on every person that enters Gokuldham. Popatlal thinks of helping Daya and Sundar.

title: Ep. 571 - Sundar In Disguise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham starts celebrating Holi. Sundar comes dressed up like a lady with Popatlal. Everyone thinks of Sundar to be Popatlal's girlfriend.

title: Ep. 572 - Friend In Need - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The whole Gokuldham and Jorawar find Sundar amidst them playing Holi. However, it was found Sundar was trying to help his friend who was in need of money. Everyone continued playing Holi post all the misunderstandings.

title: Ep. 573 - Babita Is Excited - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Mr. Iyer breaks out the news of getting promoted to Babita. Excitedly, Babita distributes sweets in Gokuldham. Later, she gets the news of them also getting transferred to Chennai.

title: Ep. 574 - Iyer's Transfer  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita and Mr. Iyer have decided to leave for Chennai. Mr. Iyer informs everyone about the same. Jethalal is upset about the news of them leaving for Chennai.

title: Ep. 575 - What To Gift? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham discusses on what to gift Mr. Iyer and Babita for their farewell. Babita expresses how much she will miss the people of Gokuldham. Jethalal decides to leave for Chennai with Daya.

title: Ep. 576 - The April Fools Prank - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal dreams of leaving for Chennai with Daya. Everyone in Gokuldham delivers a speech for Mr. Iyer and Babita's farewell. Mr. Iyer tells everyone how he made a fool out of everyone.

title: Ep. 577 - Anjali Wins A Competition - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali wins a diet food recipe competition. She plans to share her gift with all the ladies of Gokuldham. Madhvi suggests Bhide take help from Tapu to help him with the computer.

title: Ep. 578 - The Technology Master - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu helps out Bhide with a computer post which Madhvi and Bhide praise him. Taarak and friends discuss the advantages and disadvantages of the internet. Bhide gets addicted to social media.

title: Ep. 579 - Bhide Gets An Email - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide receives an email stating that they have hit a jackpot of 1 crore rupees. In order to get that money, he has to deposit a hefty amount of 50,000 rupees. Madhvi and Bhide plan to do the needful.

title: Ep. 580 - The Power of Money - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhvi and Bhide are extremely excited about the jackpot. Bhide tells her how they can become rich and can hold status in their society. Later, they receive a complimentary gift from the charitable trust.
